UID:dd5ddffe-a435-584d-85b6-458540bd90cf
DESCRIPTION:As part of planned road work\, changes are being proposed to E
 lmhurst Dr in Ward 1 Etobicoke North including new painted bike lanes. Als
 o being proposed are short new multi-use trails along Islington that would
  connect Elmhurst to The Elms Park trail. What do you think? Attend the pu
 blic meeting on April 15 and have your say! (https://www.toronto.ca/commun
 ity-people/get-involved/public-consultations/infrastructure-projects/elmhu
 rst-drive-and-islington-avenue-safety-improvements/) Learn more and comple
 te the survey.\n\n(Rendering of proposed changes to Elmhurst including pai
 nted bike lanes. Image: City of Toronto)\nURL: https://www.cycleto.ca/publ
 ic_consultation
LOCATION:St. Stephen Catholic School\n55 Golfdown Drive\nEtobicoke ON M9W 
 2H8\nCA
URL:https://www.cycleto.ca/public_consultation
END:VEVENT
